{"word":"G293 - ἀμφίβληστρον - amphíblēstron - am-fib'-lace-tron - Net","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμφίβληστρον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">amphíblēstron</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-fib'-lace-tron</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Net</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"வலை - பால்வேறுபாடு இல்லாத பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"anything thrown around one to impede his motion"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G297 - ἀμφότερος - amphóteros - am-fot'-er-os/297\">G297</a> and <a href=\"#/G906 - βάλλω - bállō - bal'-lo/906\">G906</a>; a (fishing) <i>net</i> (as <i>thrown about</i> the fish): - net.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}